    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Architraves modified by being carried around a curved opening instead of a rectangular one, specifically the continuous curved molded or decorated bands framing the face of an arch. Examples include bands stacked in a series framing a portal.</Note_Text>
